I guess I thought about it before,

01:01:05.700 --> 01:01:09.040
but reemphasized that for me,

01:01:09.840 --> 01:01:13.420
the typing is a communication tool to me,

01:01:13.860 --> 01:01:15.720
mostly through things like PyCharm,

01:01:16.160 --> 01:01:19.920
but not 100%, but mostly through the editor saying,

01:01:20.480 --> 01:01:21.540
here's what it's supposed to be here.

01:01:21.680 --> 01:01:22.820
Here's what this is supposed to do.

01:01:22.900 --> 01:01:25.440
